{"tid":632939,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3萬英呎高空引擎爆炸下墜 窗都爆埋 你會點處理","createTime":"2018-04-18T00:55:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T06:04:03.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"022755b318355261ac9206512db6070e7bb63ab7","tid":632939,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T00:55:49.000Z","msg":"美國西南航空（Southwest Airlines）紐約市拉瓜地亞機場飛往德州達拉斯的WN1380班機，周二（17日）在3萬英呎高空（約9144公尺），因為左邊引擎爆炸，而緊急降落費城國際機場，導致1死7傷。美國國家運輸安全委員會（NTSB）主席薩姆沃特（Robert Sumwalt）指，這是自2009年以來，首次有乘客在美國的航空公司客機上死亡。<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦航空總署（FAA）表示，據機長通報，客機的機身、一個引擎受損，及至少一個機窗受損，部份零件失蹤。由於窗戶破了一個洞，有乘客（部分身體）被吸出。<br />\n坐在機尾的乘客布爾曼（Amanda Bourman）表示，她在睡夢中被巨響吵醒，見到氧氣罩從天花板落下。當時，有乘客哭泣，有人說話自我安慰。她以為在劫難逃，一邊緊握丈夫的手，一邊想見女兒一面，擔心她們成為孤兒。<br />\n布爾曼又說，客機降落一刻大家都在叫喊，安全著陸後，乘客紛紛鼓掌，讚揚機長是英雄，感謝救命之恩。她見到醫護人員用心臟去顫器為一名女子急救，一名戴牛仔帽男子趕去擋住破窗。<br />\n乘客馬丁尼茲（Marty Martinez）事發時，曾在臉書上短暫直播，「我們似乎正在下墜！」他事後告訴有線新聞網（CNN）證實，當時東西從破窗飛走，一名女乘客也被吸出去，附近的乘客把她拉住。客機安全降落後，他拍下破窗圖片。<br />\n乘客特蘭欽（Matt Tranchin）稱，事發時聽到巨響，在他前三排有玻璃碎裂，空中服務員趕過去，引起混亂，「所有人都湧向穿洞的位置」。他也嗅到燒焦味，通風系統有灰噴出，然後客機開始下墜，連空服員都難掩驚慌，「有人從破窗望向引擎，不少人都哭起來」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180418/1336531/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180418%2F1336531%2F&d=ZchohgaxB9QG9V%2BAmERvXaNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=33cfbf60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180418%2F1336531%2F&h=34f00e7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180418/1336531/</a><br />\n<br />\n點塞住窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9303a2ca97b135e85bbd03755faaf0c49349ae","tid":632939,"uid":28053,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T00:59:14.000Z","msg":"吸住咗肥絲，所以塞到個窗"},{"pid":"400b1e33225edc593e707fa7ea13baf874130bf2","tid":632939,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T01:03:04.000Z","msg":"n年後又一套  xx空劫 荷里活片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f107208a2ad14f8d32c4ff241ab89b76818770","tid":632939,"uid":13149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T01:05:47.000Z","msg":"有乘客（部分身體）被吸出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3fe9c28724a6d3edbf7d83d5fee6ef4e13cf83","tid":632939,"uid":146668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T01:51:37.000Z","msg":"有無咁橋呀？"},{"pid":"4169adc1270e2aeef0616f5449a99aca9b5b9a8c","tid":632939,"uid":138319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd3fe9c28724a6d3edbf7d83d5fee6ef4e13cf83","tid":632939,"uid":146668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T01:51:37.000Z","msg":"有無咁橋呀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:41:25.000Z","msg":"就係咁橋 唔准諗 即刻答"},{"pid":"387ff372c093d32768653209d8721b418f775a64","tid":632939,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:46:26.000Z","msg":"唔好簡引擎位"},{"pid":"75bbff20ccd5d943b6e5a222ee3e31c91b5cd979","tid":632939,"uid":64056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:57:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">安全著陸後，乘客紛紛鼓掌，讚揚機長是英雄，感謝救命之恩。</span><br />\n如果係香港<br />\nd廢中同港女即刻投訴要求賠償<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600cd042d81020ef2a83ad792ec228be08cbdd20","tid":632939,"uid":39234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"400b1e33225edc593e707fa7ea13baf874130bf2","tid":632939,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T01:03:04.000Z","msg":"n年後又一套  xx空劫 荷里活片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T05:58:28.000Z","msg":"air crash investigation 又可以出多集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e12eda0b6a64987dd61fa60c18972cbe4fb0dc3","